title: Chuck Missler Exposed (religion) [xyz]
description: How dangerous it is today to believe men (and women) and what they profess... trust your Bible (if possible: avoid new age = modern bibles with the Westcott & Hort occultists text!) and be led by the Holy Spirit to teach you - do not be ignorant of "satans devices" - lest he might have an advantage of you. Search the Scriptures and pray to God the Father in the name of God the Son, Christ Jesus, and may the Holy Spirit guide us into all truth and understanding of the Bible. God bless you and keep you!
